snippet.title: Gadar 2 Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Gadar 2 Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma. Gadar 2 Featuring Sunny Deol & Ameesha Patel Directed by Anil Sharma is the Most Anticipated Sequel to 2001 Gadar which redefined Mass Cinema in Bollywood, Tara Singh is back for a New Adventure but with same Enemy & his family on the line- Will he make it or break it? Gadar 2 Full Movie Story Outline Explained & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Gadar 2 vs Omg 2 - Who is Your Winner in this Super Clash? Leave your Public Review in the Comments below.


➤ Follow Me on Instagram-
     https://www.instagram.com/thefilmiindian

➤ Follow Me on Twitter-
     https://twitter.com/thefilmiindian

#Gadar2 #Gadar2Review #Gadar2Movie

snippet.title: King of Kotha Official Trailer | Dulquer Salmaan | Abhilash Joshiy | Jakes Bejoy
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world of Kotha, watch the official trailer and enjoy the film in cinemas for August 2023 Onam release.

Cast: Dulquer Salmaan, Aishwarya Lekshmi, Dancing Rose Shabeer, Prasanna, Nyla Usha, Chemban Vinod, Gokul Suresh, Shammi Thilakn, Shanthi Krishna, Vada Chennai Saran, and Anikha Surendran

Directed by: Abhilash Joshiy
Writer: Abhilash N Chandran
Cinematography: Nimish Ravi
Music: Jakes Bejoy 
Editor: Shyam Sasidharan
Production Design: Nimesh M Thanoor
Stills: SBK
Sound Design: RESONANCE AUDIOS
Mixing: M R Rajakrishnan
Publicity Designs: NXT GEN Studio, Viyaki
Subtitles: Sherylene Rafeeque
Trailer Edit: Ruben 
Editing Team: Newton Prabhu and Srihari 

Music Composed & Arranged  by JAKES BEJOY
Lyrics for ‘Kotha Raja’ - Mu.Ri
Lead Singers  : Dabzee , Resmi Satheesh 
Music Producers :  Jakes Bejoy, Praveen Ninan, Abjaksh S , Andrew G
Chorus  :  RESMI SATEESH, ANAND SREERAJ R, AAVANI MALHAR, SONY MOHAN 
Electric Guitar - Sumesh Parameshwar 
Trumpet and Trombone : Babu 
 Session Arranged & Managed by DANIEL JOSEPH ANTONY & MANEETH MANOJ
Assisted by NAJID NIZARUDHEEN 
Premixed by - DANIEL JOSEPH ANTONY 
Music Mixed by MIDHUN ANAND 
Trailer Mixed by Rajakrishnan M R
Trailer Mastered by Gethin John @ Haffod mastering UK
Chief Associate : AKHIL J CHAND
Artist Co-ordination : KD VINCENT
Recording Engineers : MIDHUN ANAND @ Mindscore Music, VISHNU SHANKAR @ Soundtown, ROYSTER SHAJI @ Studio Benson Creation

Dolby Atmos studio: SAPTHAA RECORDS

snippet.title: Amit Shah ने Lok Sabha में CrPc संशोधन बिल किया पेश | Breaking News | PM Modi | Indian Penal Code
snippet.description:
Amit Shah ने Lok Sabha में CrPc संशोधन बिल किया पेश | Breaking News | PM Modi | Indian Penal Code

snippet.title: OMG 2 movie review | Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi, Yami Gautam | Honest Review
snippet.description:
OMG 2 is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language satirical comedy-drama film written and directed by Amit Rai. It is a spiritual sequel to OMG – Oh My God! (2012). The film stars Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi and Yami Gautam in lead roles, along with Pavan Malhotra, Govind Namdev, Arun Govil, Brijendra Kala and others. The film revolves around the subject of sex education in Indian schools. The film was theatrically released on 11 August 2023.

snippet.title: Russia launches Luna-25 mission in race to sample moon's south pole
snippet.description:
A Soyuz-2 Fregat rocket carrying a lunar landing craft blasted off on what Russia hopes will be its first successful moon landing mission in nearly 50 years. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

The unmanned Luna-25's mission to the moon that is expected to take about five days and will seek to land near the south pole of the moon, collecting geological samples from the area. India’s Chandrayaan-3 space probe entered the moon’s orbit earlier this week, and will also explore the water-rich area near the south pole.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3847: Gas Bich Mien Hui Khatam
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena assists Bhide in carrying the enormous basket of 40 kilograms of tomatoes inside the house, and Goli requests a tomato as a sign of thanks. Bhide cheerfully presents him with a plump red tomato as a symbol of appreciation. Madhvi is relieved that she can finally begin preparing her pickle for the order. Sonu and Bhide are munching on Madhvi's homemade "besan ladoos" when they hear Madhvi's voice. The father and daughter run to the kitchen to check on her and discover that a petrol cylinder needs to be fuelled this time. Bhide hurries to Sodhi's residence to acquire a replacement cylinder, but he uses a different firm. Is Madhvi going to be able to deliver the pickles on time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3847, 11 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Khali Bottle Mein Sharaab Bhar Di

(Badshah)

Ya Ya 
Ek Baat Samajh Le 
Mein Bolu Kam Aankhon Se Padhle
Game Ke Top Pe Baitha 
Jiske Bhi Bas Ki Wo Aake Pakadle 
Inse Game Crack Hi Nai Hora.. Na 
Hit Koi Track Hi Nai Hora .. Na 
Yahaan Fir Maine Scene Change Kiya 
Aur Kuch Logo Ka Come Back Hi Nai Hora.. Woo
Badshah Hai Naam Meri Jaan, 
Pyaar So Mujhko Wo Baddie Bolti Hai, Aye
Game Mein Laundo Ka Baap Hoon Baby 
Ek Tu Hi Thodi Hai Jo Mujhe Daddy Bolti Hai

(Payal Dev)

Subah Se Shaam Tak, Bas Tera Naam Lu 
Tujhko Jo Dekhu Mein Dil Apna Thaam Lu
Jo Tu Mujhe Choole Toh Badan Mein Sansani
Khudko Samjhati Hu Ke Sabar Se Kaam Lu 
Neende Meri Tune Haraam Kar Di 
Gandi Meri Tune Zabaan Kar Di 
Teri Kasam Bilkul Seedhi Sadi Thi Mein Tune Ladki Kharab Kar Di 

(Badshah)

Koi Ungli Karta Hai, Haa, Toh Mein Baanh Bhi Chadhata Hu Par Saamne Ho Bandhi Toh Mein Good Boy Ban Jaata Hoon
Ya, Udti Hai Khabare Leta Na Stress, No
Game Ka Carter On To The Next, Ho
Plane Hai Private Life Hai Blessed, Yeah
Muthi Mein Game Mere Ghante Pe Press
Badboyshah Kaise Tuje Tere Bas Ka Laga 
Na Mujhe Aisa Maska Laga 
Rahi Na Kisi Kaam Dham Ki Jabse Ladki Ko Chaska Laga Mera

Ya , Ish You Boy , It’s Your Boy Badshah 

(Payal Dev)

snippet.title: #Video | #Pawan Singh | Kashi Mein Shiv Shankar | काशी में शिव शंकर | Bol Bam Song | Sawan Ke Gana
snippet.description:
अब गुंजेगा शिव जी का डंका हर गल्ली हर मोहल्ला जब बजेगा #Powerstar #Pawan Singh का ई गाना "काशी में शिव शंकर" 🙏🔥

Credits : 
🎤Singer - Pawan Singh
✍️Lyrics - Bhagirath Pathak
🎶Music - Shubham Raj SBR
💃Feat -  Soumya Pandey 
🎥Director - Ravi Pandit 
🤔Parikalpana - Deepak Singh
🤝Help - Vicky Singh , Amit Singh,Abhay Pandey
🙏Ashirvad - Mata pita , Ajit singh Jokhari

Lyrics :

मुखड़ा =बहेला जहांवा पावन गंगा धारा ....... हर हर महादेव बोले लोगवा सारा
नाथो के नाथ जहां विश्वनाथ स्व्यम बइठी ध्यान धरेले........... (ॐ नमः पार्वती पत्तेय हर हर महादेव)
काशी के कंकड़ कंकड़ में शिव शंकर वास करेले.......

अंतरा=भूमि ह ई संत सन्यासी के
ज्योतिर्लिंग बा ईहा कैलाशी के
नाही काल से डेराला महकाल के चेला 
कष्ट कट जाला जोगिया के नाम जे लेला .....
सीधे ऊ जाला मोक्ष द्वार ईहा मर के जे भी जरेले........ काशी के कंकड़ कंकड़

अंतरा=पवन भजन गावेले शिव शक्ति के ......
हर्षत भागीरथ भाव भक्ति के
खुद अपने से जाके श्मशान कगरी
सारा देहिया में भस्मी भभूत रगरी 
खाली ना लौटे कोई ऊहा से सबके झोली भरेले.....
काशी के कंकड़ कंकड़ में.......

snippet.title: Thai Sticky Rice Recipe in Tamil | Sticky Rice with Mango | Dessert Recipes in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make thai sticky rice recipe in tamil. In this recipe I am going to compare making the recipe with thailand sticky rice as well as with our regular rice. The extra gluten in thai rice make is very stretchy and sticky once it is steamed. Sticky rice can be served in both sweet and savory recipes. The texture of the rice pairs well with other contrasting tastes and textures also the steamed rice has a mild sweetness to it.
#stickyricerecipe #mangostickyrice #thairecipe 

Friends, please do try this thai sticky rice recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

snippet.title: पीएम के भाषण में का बा | PM speaks in the parliament
snippet.description:
अपने विद्यार्थी जीवन में ऐसे कई छात्रों को देखा है, जो परीक्षा में जवाब नहीं आने पर भी पूरा पन्ना भर कर आ जाते थे। प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी ने सवा दो घंटे से अधिक समय तक भाषण दिया है। इस भाषण में मणिपुर कितना था, जो था, वो कितना सही था, विपक्ष को घेरने के लिए जिन तथ्यों और घटनाओं का उल्लेख किया गया, उनमें कितनी बातें सही हैं, कितनी झूठ हैं और कितनी आधी-अधूरी हैं ये जानने के लिए आवश्यकता है ऐसे युवाओं की जो प्रधानमंत्री मोदी के भाषण से सही और ग़लत का पता लगा सकें। कभी वे 60 के दशक में जाते हैं तो कभी 80 के दशक में, अपने कार्यकाल के दशक में नहीं जाते हैं कि उनके रहते मणिपुर की हालत क्यों हुई? सवा दो घंटे के भाषण में प्रधानमंत्री मणिपुर पर क़रीब चार मिनट बोले हैं। आप उनके बाक़ी के भाषण को संसद की वेबसाइट पर देख-पढ़ कर ख़ुद फैसला करें।

localized.title: पीएम के भाषण में का बा | PM speaks in the parliament
localized.description:
अपने विद्यार्थी जीवन में ऐसे कई छात्रों को देखा है, जो परीक्षा में जवाब नहीं आने पर भी पूरा पन्ना भर कर आ जाते थे। प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी ने सवा दो घंटे से अधिक समय तक भाषण दिया है। इस भाषण में मणिपुर कितना था, जो था, वो कितना सही था, विपक्ष को घेरने के लिए जिन तथ्यों और घटनाओं का उल्लेख किया गया, उनमें कितनी बातें सही हैं, कितनी झूठ हैं और कितनी आधी-अधूरी हैं ये जानने के लिए आवश्यकता है ऐसे युवाओं की जो प्रधानमंत्री मोदी के भाषण से सही और ग़लत का पता लगा सकें। कभी वे 60 के दशक में जाते हैं तो कभी 80 के दशक में, अपने कार्यकाल के दशक में नहीं जाते हैं कि उनके रहते मणिपुर की हालत क्यों हुई? सवा दो घंटे के भाषण में प्रधानमंत्री मणिपुर पर क़रीब चार मिनट बोले हैं। आप उनके बाक़ी के भाषण को संसद की वेबसाइट पर देख-पढ़ कर ख़ुद फैसला करें।

Episode 3846: Padosi Ne Ki Padosi Ki Madad
--------------------------------------------------------
Inspector Panday chooses to take Popatlal into custody even though no one is prepared to accept that he is a thief. The police constables pick up Popatlal from his house and bring him to the society's compound. Inspector Chaalu Pandey confronts the auto-rickshaw driver to repeat his statement of how he had helped Popatlal in shifting the tomato basket in the office later, Popatlal explains what exactly occurred to everyone. Will Inspector Panday accept his story?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3846, 10 Aug 2023

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 29 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 8th Aug 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Sirf Tum Episode 27 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 10th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

snippet.description:

#urdu1 #sencalkapimi #dastakmayraydilpay 

Dastak Mayray Dil Pay Episode 118 Turkish Drama in Urdu Dubbing also called Sencal Kapimi dated 11th August 2023

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

----

#chandryaan3 #isro #chandryan 

Chandrayaan 3 ने भेजा संदेश, हर हिंदुस्तानी को सुनना चाहिए | ISRO | Chandrayaan-3 updates | Chandrayaan 3 live | Chandrayaan 3 Update

चंद्रयान 3 (Chandrayaan 3) ने कमाल कर दिया है...इसरो (ISRO) के साथ पूरी दुनिया को जिस पल का इंतजार था...वो पल अब आ गया है... Chandrayaan-3 ने अग्निपरिक्षा को पास कर लिया है...भारत के लिए ये किसी बड़ी जीत से कम नहीं है...भारत की अंतरिक्ष में बढ़ती धमक की सबसे बड़ी खबर चंद्रमा के ऑर्बिट से आई है.... 5 जुलाई को Chandrayaan 3 ने जैसे ही चांद की कक्षा में कदम रखा, उसने धरती पर इसरो सेंटर को सबसे पहले जो संदेश भेजा उसे हर भारतीय को जरूर सुनना चाहिए

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 28 Teaser - 10th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3845 | 9 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3845: Nau Do Gyaara
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bhide fails to discover the tomatoes after a frantic search in Gokuldham, he decides to file a police report. After some time has passed, Chalu Pandey arrives at the society to look into the missing tomatoes. Bhide tells the entire story of how he had been protecting the tomatoes all night and how they vanished the instant he returned home. Chalu Pandey deduces from the sequence of events that someone from the Gokuldham had stolen them. The residents of Gokuldham are outraged, but Bhide assures the cop that we don't doubt them. Chalu Pandey's inquiry continues, and this time he suspects the newspaper person. Will Chalu Pandey apprehend the perpetrator?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3845, 9 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show:

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: OMG 2 (BIASED) REVIEW | What have you done Bollywood?!! - Totally Unexpected !! | Akash Banerjee
snippet.description:
In a refreshing departure from Bollywood medeocracy, "OMG 2" takes a daring leap into the realm of Sex Education, a topic often shrouded in silence and taboo within Indian society. This cinematic gem is a courageous and important step towards discussing teenage issues, sexuality & societal relations. 

The film is a masterful blend of entertainment and education, skilfully presenting a subject matter that many might shy away from. Though Oh My God - 2 is a Akshay Kumar starrer - the movie is largely carried by the brilliant Pankaj Tripathi. 

Never in history of 'The Deshbhakt' have we ever recommended a movie - but this one is a sure shot watch! Because when Bollywood does deliver - people don't bother to watch.

snippet.title: Allah De Bandeya | B Praak | Jaani | Aly Goni | Jasmine Bhasin | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents 'Allah De Bandeya,' the third music video from B Praak’s debut album “Zoharajabeen.” Immerse yourself in the warmth of B Praak's voice, as Jaani's heart-touching lyrics tell a story of being more than a friend or lover, but a comforting home for someone. The music, tenderly composed by Kartik Dev and artfully arranged by Mir Desai, complements the song's emotive resonance.

Starring the captivating duo of Jasmine Bhasin and Aly Goni, the short film, directed by Arvindr Khaira, weaves a visual narrative that illustrates the transformative power of unconditional love. It explores the profound impact such love can have, showing that when you've found "your person," nothing else in the world matters. 

Listen to 'Allah De Bandeya' and all the hits from "Zohrajabeen" - http://www.umgindia.lnk.to/Zohrajabeen
